Test 1: Immutable point operations
Created ImmutablePoint(10, 20)
p1: (10, 20)
Creating new point: (10+5, 20+3)
Created ImmutablePoint(15, 23)
p2 (p1 + (5,3)): (15, 23)
p1 unchanged: (10, 20)
Creating scaled point: (10*2, 20*2)
Created ImmutablePoint(20, 40)
p3 (p1 * 2): (20, 40)
p1 still unchanged: (10, 20)

Test 2: Immutable person
Created ImmutablePoint(100, 200)
Created ImmutablePerson: Alice, age 30
person1: Alice (age 30) at (100, 200)

Test 3: Create modified person
Creating person with new age: 31
Created ImmutablePerson: Alice, age 31
person2: Alice (age 31) at (100, 200)
person1 unchanged: Alice (age 30) at (100, 200)

Test 4: Change location
Created ImmutablePoint(300, 400)
Creating person with new location
Created ImmutablePerson: Alice, age 30
person3: Alice (age 30) at (300, 400)
person1 still unchanged: Alice (age 30) at (100, 200)
